    "data_year": 2026,
    "update_date": "2026-04-05",
    "note": "This benchmark is under construction. Each rating must be backed by direct policy quotes and URLs. Confidence intervals reflect uncertainty. If a company's policy is not publicly available or unclear, that is reflected in the rating.",
